===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{context|derogatory|lang=en}} One who [[advocate]]s a certain course of action, often of [[political]] or [[social]] concern, in the [[unreflected]] [[conviction]] of their own [[moral]] [[superiority]].
#: ''Prohibition in the United States was an unsuccessful attempt by '''do-gooders''' to save people from the dangers of alcohol, whether they wanted to be saved or not.''

